        {
            "title": "IF Function Practice",
            "content": "<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">Practice: Creating Categories</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">Create a new sheet named 'IF Practice':</p><div class=\"image-frame bg-gray-600 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-4\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cpWB3TB.png\" alt=\"Screenshot of how to add a new spreadsheet sheet\" /></div><div class=\"exercise-container bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Activity 1: Group Size Categories</h3><p class=\"mb-2\">Create a new column that categorizes groups as 'Small' (1-2 people) or 'Large' (3+ people). Copy your formula and results to your 'IF Practice' sheet.</p><div class=\"mt-4\"><button class=\"in-tutorial-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-2 bg-blue-600 bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-30 transition-colors duration-200\"><span class=\"text-blue-400 font-semibold\">View Solution</span><svg class=\"toggle-arrow w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform duration-200\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\" /></svg></button><div class=\"in-tutorial-toggle-content bg-gray-800 rounded-lg mt-2 p-4\"><div class=\"image-frame bg-gray-600 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-4\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JTn1Of4.png\" alt=\"IF function example\" /></div><div class=\"formula mb-4\"><span class=\"key operator\">=</span>IF(<span class=\"cell-ref\">G2</span><=2, \"Small\", \"Large\")</div></div></div></div><div class=\"exercise-container bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Activity 2: Group Status</h3><p class=\"mb-2\">Create a column that shows 'Newsletter' for people who signed up, 'No Newsletter' for those who didn't. Copy your formula and results to your 'IF Practice' sheet.</p></div>",
